###Basic knowledge
( ´◔ ‸◔')
##Layers: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Window_manager#/media/File:Schema_of_the_layers_of_the_graphical_user_interface.svg
1. X: Xorg: Display server: 

    Display layer(Display server): Xorg (Or KWin)
               |
              \|/
    ------------------------------
              Kernel


2. WM: i3: Tiling Window Manager:

    Display layer(Display server): Xorg -----> WM: I3(or awesome)
               |
              \|/
    ------------------------------
              Kernel
    i3: Use xcb instead of Xlib.
    
    
    
    
    
    
    
    
    
    
    
    
    
    
    
    
